### Event Streaming API Tests
### Tests for EventStreamingController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096
### Note: These endpoints use Server-Sent Events (SSE)

### Subscribe to session events
### Opens an SSE connection to receive session-specific events
### Note: This is an SSE endpoint - connection stays open
### Events include: session status, message updates, tool executions, etc.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache
Connection: keep-alive

###

### Subscribe to global events
### Opens an SSE connection to receive global/project-wide events
### Note: This is an SSE endpoint - connection stays open
### Events include: project updates, file changes, VCS changes, etc.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/global
Accept: text/event-stream
Cache-Control: no-cache
Connection: keep-alive

###
